window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Lunatics, anarchists, and mad bombers—they stand no chance against Doctor Undying!</b></p> <p>Even after reuniting with my beloved, the villainess Green Phoenix, the work of an immortal is never done. Learning of a plot to take over the world using my old mind control virus, I know I must act.</p> <p>For the virus is a fake, a ruse to hide my magnum opus—the genophage that unlocked the potential of the human genome and led to the current age of parahumans. If someone were to learn the truth, they could undo my greatest work or worse.</p> <p><b>Gathering my villainesses, we embark on a world-spanning quest, battling against drugged-out cultists, multi-level marketing schemes, and a serial killer bent on bloody revenge. I’ll let nothing threaten the future I have set for humanity!</b></p>"; 
